scoringPlays.text: Anthoula Kelly 70 Yd Interception Return (Asa Fuller Kick)
Kyle Williams 3 Yd pass from Manny Wilkins (Brandon Ruiz Kick)
Eno Benjamin 17 Yd Run (Brandon Ruiz Kick)
Marcus McMaryion 10 Yd Run (Asa Fuller Kick)
Ronnie Rivers 68 Yd Run (Asa Fuller Kick)
Ronnie Rivers 5 Yd Run (Asa Fuller Kick)

videos.description: Anthoula Kelly jumps a route and makes multiple men miss on a 70-yard pick-6, putting Fresno State up 10-0.
videos.headline: Kelly dodges everyone on 70-yard pick-6

videos.description: Manny Wilkins dumps it off to Kyle Williams, who flips into the end zone to put Arizona State on the board.
videos.headline: Williams flips into end zone

videos.description: Eno Benjamin breaks off two big runs in a row to punch it into the end zone, giving Arizona State its first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Benjamin's back-to-back big gains give ASU lead

videos.description: QB Marcus McMaryion takes it himself for a 10-yard touchdown, putting Fresno State back in front 17-14.
videos.headline: Fresno State's QB sneak puts it back in front

videos.description: Dejonte O'Neal dives towards the pylon but loses the ball midair to result in a touchback against Fresno State.
videos.headline: Fresno State's fumble results in touchback

videos.description: Ronnie Rivers breaks free for a 68-yard touchdown, giving Fresno State the 24-20 lead.
videos.headline: Fresno State takes lead on Rivers' 68-yard TD

videos.description: Ronnie Rivers muscles his way into the end zone for his second touchdown, putting him over 150 rushing yards for the game.
videos.headline: Rivers' 2nd TD puts him over 150 rushing yards
